<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17470225-25">
               <interp inst="t17470225-25" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17470225-25" type="year" value="1747"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17470225-25" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17470225"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17470225-25" type="date" value="17470225"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17470225-25-off111-c274" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470225-25-defend330 t17470225-25-off111 t17470225-25-verdict112"></join>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17470225-25-off111-c275" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470225-25-defend332 t17470225-25-off111 t17470225-25-verdict113"></join>
         
               <p>157, 158. 
               
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-defend330" type="defendantName">
                     Timothy 
                     Aldridge 
                  <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend330" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend330" type="given" value="Timothy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend330" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             and 
               
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-defend332" type="defendantName">
                     Robert 
                     Aldridge 
                  <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend332" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend332" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-defend332" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             were indicted for <rs id="t17470225-25-off111" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-off111" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-off111" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one Copper Porridge pot, value 7 s one Brass Ladle, value 2 d.
            </rs> the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-victim334" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Roberts 
                  <interp inst="t17470225-25-victim334" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-victim334" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-victim334" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470225-25-off111 t17470225-25-victim334"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-person335">
                  Sarah 
                  Roberts 
               <interp inst="t17470225-25-person335" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person335" type="given" value="Sarah"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person335" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . the principle Witness, who deposed (she keeps the George and Bull in Orchard street) that the Prisoners came into her House, and called for a Pint of Beer; after they had been in the House some Time, they went backward into the Yard, then came again into the Room; afterwards two of them went out into the Street; about a quarter of an Hour after she missed her Pot; there were three of the Boys, but one was run away. 
               <persName id="t17470225-25-person336">
                  Timothy 
                  Aldridge 
               <interp inst="t17470225-25-person336" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person336" type="given" value="Timothy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person336" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was in the House all the Time; and 
               <persName id="t17470225-25-person337">
                  Robert 
                  Aldridge 
               <interp inst="t17470225-25-person337" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person337" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person337" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             confessed, when he was taken, that he had sold the Pot, but it was stole by the other Boy, that was run away.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-person338">
                  Timothy 
                  Aldridge 
               <interp inst="t17470225-25-person338" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person338" type="given" value="Timothy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person338" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             
                  <rs id="t17470225-25-verdict112" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-verdict112" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs>;</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17470225-25-person339">
                  Robert 
                  Aldridge 
               <interp inst="t17470225-25-person339" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person339" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-person339" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             
                  <rs id="t17470225-25-verdict113" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-verdict113" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-verdict113" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17470225-25-punish114" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470225-25-punish114" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470225-25-defend332 t17470225-25-punish114"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
